'''Charlie Richard''' ([[May 30]], [[1941]] &ndash; [[December 13]], [[1994]] ) was a head [[college football|football]] coach at [[Baker University]]. He was inducted into the [[College Football Hall of Fame]] in 2004 and the Kansas Sports Hall of Fame in 2006.

